1. ID and textbox    ---- ID in <label> tag and textbox in <input> tag + type is "text"
2. Name and textbox    ---- Name in <label> tag and textbox in <input> tag + type is "text"
3. Description and textarea ---- Description in <label> tag and textarea in <input> tag + type attribute nahi hoga
4. Date and date ---- Date in <label> tag and date in <input> tag + type is "date"
5. Color and pallete ---- Color in <label> tag and color in <input> tag + type attribute nahi hoga

Bootsrtap Classes : 
div --- form-control
label -- form-label
input -- form-control
